174
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,000
Máte pravdu.

175
00:13:46,130 --> 00:13:47,090
Pane Romeo?

176
00:13:47,590 --> 00:13:48,680
Ah, ano?

177
00:13:49,470 --> 00:13:51,600
Jste v pořádku?

178
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,810
Vůně růží je zde silná.

179
